OL,3,CHopes that the two child benefit cap
OL,4,Cwill be scrapped
OL,6,FShe said: "I've seen and heard mams
OL,7,Ftalk about how they're struggling.
OL,8,FIt's awful... but it's just how life
OL,9,Fis I'm afraid.
OL,11,F"They're not asking for thousands,
OL,12,Fthey're just asking for enough to feed
OL,13,Fand bring their child up like all the
OL,14,Fothers. What they're asking for is
OL,15,Fjust enough."
