OL,3,CHopes that the two child benefit cap
OL,4,Cwill be scrapped
OL,6,F"That child doesn't ask to be born
OL,7,Fthird or fourth... they don't stand a
OL,8,Fchance, some of these children."
OL,10,FAs Christmas fast approaches, the work
OL,11,Fof the Moorclose Community Centre has
OL,12,Fintensified, and Angela is now
OL,13,Fdetermined to ensure the children of
OL,14,Fher clients do not go without on the
OL,15,Fbig day.
OL,17,FShe said: "In some families, they just
OL,18,Fdon't have enough to make ends meet.
OL,19,FWe just do what we can to try and
OL,20,Fhelp, whether food or presents.
