OL,3,CHopes that the two child benefit cap
OL,4,Cwill be scrapped
OL,6,F"We hand out presents, or items with
OL,7,Ftags and wrapping paper, so their
OL,8,Fchild gets the same Christmas as the
OL,9,Fchild next door. We'll just do
OL,10,Fwhatever we can to help - that's what
OL,11,Fwe're here for."
OL,13,FAngela, just like the parents she
OL,14,Fhelps at the centre, will be eagerly
OL,15,Fwatching to see what plans Ms Reeves
OL,16,Fhas for the two child benefit cap.
OL,18,FMany families across our region will
OL,19,Fbe doing the same.
